{"title":"我在燃烧","authors":["张楚琨"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张楚琨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把往日的恋念抛弃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上前，投身在熊熊的烈火里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不可抗御的火力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧着我的灵魂，我的心，我的形体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带烟的眼睛，从痉挛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窥见了自由的、广阔的天地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤凰呵，生命的神奇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毁灭自己又创造自己！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细胞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在不朽的共同体中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你便是他，他便是你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你和整体分离，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便不再具有生命力；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在整体中却坚强无比！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是微小的而又伟大的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此，你最大的幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乃是为集体而战斗，为集体！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个体的消亡有什么关系呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你已把永生的歌献给自己。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}